latestIgtvVideos.title: Sol de Janeiro Giving Back 🇧🇷
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Brazil lies at the center of all we do at Sol de Janeiro, it is our home, inspiration, and heart. We love sharing the joyful Brazilian spirit with you all, but we also have a responsibility to give back to our home.
 
This is why we are honored to be working with Solar Meninos de Luz (@meninosdeluz), a nonprofit school committed to transforming the lives of children and adolescents in situations of social vulnerability in the communities of Cantagalo and Pavão-Pavãozinho in Rio. At Sol de Janeiro we believe that education is the most powerful weapon we have to make the world a better place, and are a proud supporter of this organization and cause.
